Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.67,0:00:02.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After being separated all \Nof a sudden from Cana,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:07.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thrown into a battle with one of \Nthe 7 Kin of Purgatory, Kain Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and I joined the battle halfway, but \NNatsu didn't really get a chance to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:18.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the new special move I came up \Nwith, we raked a big white dumpling over the coals!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Special move, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pulling as hard as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait... Can't you just break \Nthe rocks with your fire, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.51,0:02:17.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Light and darkness, mixed together...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who will lead the way \Nto the shining red tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairies or Demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:35.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose hearts will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic blades?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can summon weapons as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's body is made of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter the attack, Juvia will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:02.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia's body made of water... was injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My blades attack the sense of pain directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they are "sensory blades".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be one of the 7 Kin of Purgatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not deem answering that as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe out the enemy. That is my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead-End of Despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been taken away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have spread something around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't follow her like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta search for Cana, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you lifting your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... Maybe I'll take a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Cana too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:01.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we have to go after Zeref now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I just explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to use \NZeref to change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just way over-the-top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna live in a world \Nthat's just full of fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:23.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make sure to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They hurt Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys better not think \NI'll let them off this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Off the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:40.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! They must have a ship somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:44.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman from before said something about \Nbringing Zeref back to their master, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good chance that their ship \Nis anchored somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:50.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref is being taken there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, search for their ship from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:58.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks... like I'm out of magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess you're just \Na widdle kitty cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:05.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, how about we go back \Nto where Wendy and Gramps is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can ask Carla and Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:15.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Route E, where the first \Ntest of the exam took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:27.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave of Mavis, the founding master \Nof Fairy Tail, is somewhere in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll climb into first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:31.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become an S class wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I'm an S class wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, they never show up \Nwhen you search for 'em...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:05.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are these 7 Kin of Purgatory guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that Cana sure was in a foul mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she run out of booze and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:23.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I haven't seen \Nher drink since we got to Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she going cold turkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, you'll return to being \Nthe true king, Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref? That man she's \Ncarrying on her shoulder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Grimoire Heart... She's my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:12.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like her... Like my teacher, Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is wondrous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in quite \Nthe good mood, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,3 of my 7 Kin of Purgatory \Nhave been defeated, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:47.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those spawn of Makarov's \Nhave done quite well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is it my turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:55.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... This is not a battle \Nfor you to join, Bluenote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to be able to \Nplay around a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let my body go soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:26.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? If I sink the ship, then they \Nwon't be able to find it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to expose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov's brood will gather here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:36.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,unaware they've fallen \Ninside the demon's maw...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:41.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you eat any prey that \Nhasn't been led into your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will head out for my meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you go, the land will rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:54.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are down to four... Almost half.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:59.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If another falls... I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today seems like a day I \Ncan stretch my wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluenote Stinger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who singlehandedly destroyed \Nthe Blue Dragon Regiment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,led by Commander Ghora \Nduring the Cabria war...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:28.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The great wizard who is said not \Nto even leave weeds in his wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A big fish like that was in Grimoire Heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They are no longer an opponent \Nthat we can handle ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the same goes for Fairy Tail, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us contact headquarters at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is now beyond our purview.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dranbalt-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He even took the communications \Nlacrima with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be late contacting headquarters now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world are \Nyou thinking, Dranbalt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elsewhere in a corner of \NTenroujima is Makarov,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who was gravely injured by \NHades in a fierce battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, Lily, and Carla are looking after \Nhim, while waiting for Natsu to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy-san, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the Master doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:39.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His wounds are just too severe, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:43.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange... I don't sense \Nthat his life is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:47.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's some secret to this \Nso-called "Sacred Ground"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you run off to, jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Mest, from the Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My real name is Dranbalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.73,0:11:02.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dranbalt-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to rescue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:23.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With my magic, I can evacuate just the \NFairy Tail members from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can figure out where \Neveryone is somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna have to pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to ask the \NMagic Council to save us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:41.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a problem for our guild, and we're \Ngonna deal with these guys ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If headquarters finds out what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a good chance \Nthey'll fire on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna shoot Etherion again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you guys ever learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's some destructive magic \Nthat's seriously powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:05.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It struck us while we were \Nat the Tower of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm impressed you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:14.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure of the details, but if \NI recall, lacrima absorbed it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:19.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guild just faces crises \Nwherever it goes, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they fire that on us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be sure what will happen, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we just have to finish things up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:32.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov's down! And Grimoire Heart \Nstill has fearsome people left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:34.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now... So that's why you're \Ngonna blow up the whole island?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This island is our guild's sacred ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The grave of the founding \Nmaster is here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't take you attacking this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you won't get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna protect the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to threaten us? The Magic Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just some wizard guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen carefully, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:05.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a crap whether it's \NGrimoire Heart or the Magic Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who lays a hand on \Nour guild is the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:34.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This air... I feel a storm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:46.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting aside the fact we used \Nup our magic power for the exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we're having such a \Nhard time when it's two against one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back. I will defeat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza Scarlet... You are number 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 4 of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:09.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth most important member \Nto kill, by my reckoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is quite important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you aiming for Juvia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 13 is weak trash,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so better to clean it up first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:35.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 3 is Gildarts, but he no \Nlonger seems to be on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:39.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 2 is Makarov, however he seems \Nto have been defeated by Lord Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The master is number 2?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:46.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying there's someone \Nmore important than the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 1 is Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Fullbuster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:15:01.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... the man who killed Ultear's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He caused Ultear to suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:11.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the man who hurt my Ultear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive him! I'll \Ntear him limb from limb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forgive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Juvia's line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:41.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose life were you planning to take, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her? She's only number 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Calm down, Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm... down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:58.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is aiming for Gray-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And for some irrational reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think... Juvia can stay calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:09.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will never forgive this girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Nebula!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a totally different person \Nthan the one I fought during the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her strong feelings for her \Nloved one become her strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:43.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Juvia's true power...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san, please leave this to Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and find Wendy and the \Nothers. And Gray-sama, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let number 4 get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maguilty Lese!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:25.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their main camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where Grimoire Heart's master is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:43.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tears put out of mind my own desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The evil-eye wriggles \Nimpatiently in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:48.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from some song, Rusty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the scream of a shattered heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:57.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuma, you're quite beat up. For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof that I fought someone strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do at all. There isn't \Nanyone like that in this guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart's fragment wavers not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:15.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't underestimate Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their weapon is not their magic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the ability to turn their \Nconviction into a blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:24.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Conviction into a blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:28.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems very much like our Meldy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's the same human, Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of us holds hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the other holds love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's the same person, the different \Nfeelings cause him to be seen differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A symbol of individuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what makes us human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here for the purpose of killing Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was able to meet with a person \Nwho feels strongly for Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:07.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings for Gray will kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia... I will show you a little bit \Nof heaven, and a great sea of despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, think of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Picture the one you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sense Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:40.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maguilty Sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia and Gray's senses are now one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:59.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only connect them if one's feelings \Nfor the other is strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Juvia and Gray-sama are... one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your senses, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all light headed all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your two senses are fully linked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is in heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will die in agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, this magic only shares pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pain you experience is felt by Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:42.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to hurt Gray-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:47.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her magic power continues to rise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was this powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:54.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her feelings are giving her strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:59.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll show you the \Npower of feelings myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Spread Sense Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Juvia hurt too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:43.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for Ultear... I don't \Nneed this life of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:48.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used you as a relay, and \Nnow I am linked to my target.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:56.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia, Gray, and my senses \Nare all linked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:22:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, no matter which one of \Nus dies, Gray will die, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the dead-end of despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The dead-end of Gray's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a heart of affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.94,0:23:59.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's wrong, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.75,0:24:02.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is the feeling of wanting \Nto protect someone dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:01.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:03.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Are you listening, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:04.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is an overflowing passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two, lead to a fateful encounter, their \Nfeelings deeply entwined, play a single tune together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I've got fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ooh, Carla's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly a love swimphony! {sic}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:11.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.32,0:24:12.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}His head's gone off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.90,0:24:16.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Love and the Tears of Vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.91,0:24:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screwed it up, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:21.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't mispronounce it! I was \Njust twalking wike a nwative!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:25.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, fine, got it. Just slow down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:27.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
